# Maintainer playbook (local only)

Copy this file to **`MAINTAINER.md`** in the bundle root. `MAINTAINER.md` is gitignored — do not commit org names, internal repo slugs, or machine-specific paths.

## Local setup

| Field | Your value |
|-------|------------|
| `WORKFLOWS_BUNDLE_PATH` | e.g. `~/Repos/lsi/current/cursor-dev-workflows` |
| Adopter repos | `video-encoder`, `web`, `agents/ai-agent` |
| Layout | **LSI only** — `.lsi/workflows/` (see [docs/adoption-layout.md](docs/adoption-layout.md)) |

## Adopt / re-sync loop

After every bundle release (`VERSION` + tag):

```bash
cd "$WORKFLOWS_BUNDLE_PATH"

for target config; do
  # video-encoder
  python3 snippets/adopt.py --target ../video-encoder --config patches/video-encoder.yaml --accept-policy-defaults
  # web
  python3 snippets/adopt.py --target ../web --config patches/web.yaml --accept-policy-defaults
  # ai-agent monorepo
  python3 snippets/adopt.py --target ../agents/ai-agent --config patches/ai-agent.yaml --accept-policy-defaults
done
```

First adopt on a repo with drift: run `--audit-only` first, commit `patches/files/<repo>/audit-resolutions.yaml`, then adopt.

## Verify all adopters

```bash
for repo in ../video-encoder ../web ../agents/ai-agent; do
  python3 snippets/verify-adopters.py --repo-root "$repo"
done
```

Individual checks:

```bash
python3 snippets/adoption-verify-links.py --repo-root ../web --canonical .lsi/workflows
python3 snippets/audit-agent-docs.py --repo-root ../web --fail-on error
```

## CI: `check_version.py`

Adopt copies `scripts/check_version.py` — **pipelines are not auto-edited**. Snippets:

| Repo | File | Version file |
|------|------|----------------|
| video-encoder | `bitbucket-pipelines.yml` (existing) | `version.txt` |
| web | [docs/ci/check_version-web.yml](docs/ci/check_version-web.yml) | `version.txt` |
| ai-agent | [docs/ci/check_version-ai-agent.yml](docs/ci/check_version-ai-agent.yml) | `VERSION` (`VERSION_FILE=VERSION`) |

## Pre-release checklist (bundle)

- [ ] Update `## [Unreleased]` in [CHANGELOG.md](CHANGELOG.md)
- [ ] Run `python3 snippets/verify-adopters.py` on each adopter after adopt dry-run
- [ ] Classify bump per [docs/versioning.md](docs/versioning.md)

## Release checklist (bundle)

- [ ] `## [X.Y.Z] - YYYY-MM-DD` in CHANGELOG; set [VERSION](VERSION)
- [ ] Tag `vX.Y.Z` on `main`
- [ ] Re-sync all adopters; open app-repo PRs with `BUNDLE_VERSION` bump in `PROJECT.md`
